RtspClient - zhjinrui.com.rtsppullclientdemo中的类
RTSP 拉流客户端: RFC 2326
Pull streaming from RTSP server, Callback when received RTP packet, Support RTP/UDP & RTP Over TCP both
连接RTSP服务器取流并在收到视频UDP包数据后回调，支持UDP和RTSP Over TCP两种模式 使用方法： RtspClient rtspClient = new RtspClient("192.168.1.100", 554, "user name", "password", "h264/main/ch1/av_stream", new RtspClient.RtspClientCallback() { @Override public void onPacket(byte[] packet, int len) { // now we get a raw RTP packet Log.i("RTSPClient", "Get RTP packet: " + len + " bytes"); }   @Override public void onResponse(List headers, byte[] body) { // now we get a RTSP response Log.i("RTSPClient", "RTSP Response: " + String.join("\r\n", headers)); } });   rtspClient.udpMode = true; rtspClient.start(); rtspClient.pause(); rtspClient.play("180.000-", 1); // Play start from 180 seconds, and normal speed rtspClient.stop();
RtspClient(String, int, String, String, String, RtspClientCallback) - 类 的构造器zhjinrui.com.rtsppullclientdemo.RtspClient
构造函数，初始化RtspClient实例

构造函数，初始化RTSP实例
